{"tid":105843,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"魔戒佛羅多阿拉崗勒苟拉斯飯局重聚合照","createTime":"2017-02-03T07:58:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-03T15:41:37.000Z","uid":41343,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a8e4165fdd2c2631767e0677efbf9fb497b88975","tid":105843,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T07:58:25.000Z","msg":"近日電影「魔戒」演員多明尼莫納漢（Dominic Monahan）在IG上PO出一張飯局照片，當年扮演精靈弓箭手的奧蘭多布魯（Orlando Bloom）、「哈比人」伊利亞伍德（Elijah Wood）、多明尼莫納漢（Dominic Monahan）和比利包依德（Billy Boyd），及在片中飾演遊俠亞拉岡的維高摩頓遜（Viggo Mortensen），手拿刀叉扮起「魔戒」中手持武器的姿勢搞笑，令人噴飯。多明尼莫納漢給這張照片的圖說是「前方有個洞穴巨人」。<br />\n<br />\n照片PO出後讓許多「魔戒」粉絲不盡回首，表示「懷念」、「魔戒週年快樂」、「遠征隊準備在出發了」、「都老了，還打得贏洞穴巨人嗎？」<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ui74k5rb\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fui74k5rb&h=d28d2147&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f718008c0d59a0455c3828241b159493f506c82e","tid":105843,"uid":29273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T08:55:35.000Z","msg":"王子佬左咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1bafc50904c8a3ad9ad668963f68ee92fde0ae4","tid":105843,"uid":6721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T09:31:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>王子佬左咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你唔講我認唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f535f3593f92ba5f19e5eb042b814907b461b75","tid":105843,"uid":24512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T09:34:57.000Z","msg":"有無人可以講下邊個係阿拉崗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係認唔到"},{"pid":"80f8f8a8b3116ad6a30f02047baa607e8e494a7e","tid":105843,"uid":58101,"like":0,